OPTION 2: Commercial Licence
================================================================================

If the AGPL-3.0 obligations do not work for your situation — for example,
you want to ship a closed-source product that uses Kaption code, or you
need a contractual warranty, indemnity, or support agreement — a separate
commercial licence is available.

See LICENSE-COMMERCIAL for an outline of typical terms and how to request
one. Commercial enquiries are uncommon for an end-user desktop tool of
this size, so please contact us before assuming you need this option;
many uses fit comfortably under AGPL-3.0.

